先 唔係你第日會後悔<br />\n除非你已經搵到人生目標"},{"pid":"9f0dab1d649e87bf4cc8ca383e8cd3a79b166885","tid":2511611,"uid":396652,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T07:15:49.000Z","msg":"雖然quit嘅話好似嘥咗兩年，但如果讀得太痛苦同埋出到嚟又唔想做本行嘅就quit，好過繼續浪費多兩年。之後再搵其他有興趣嘅嘢學可能對你仲好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f66f0ad13f4054c0b86d770fc2a7b90c74ffeb2f","tid":2511611,"uid":249015,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"26be7d0a8bc031869dd20eadac7cff8dc3fc2fa2","tid":2511611,"uid":248035,"like":0,"dislike":32,"score":-32,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T06:55:48.000Z","msg":"今年YR 2.. HKU science major Environmental Sci ...根本都無興趣, 都係阿媽話好.... QUIT...又怕令屋企人失望, 唔QUIT...又要捱多2年..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T07:16:09.000Z","msg":"除非你已經有哂真係好既計劃<br />\n唔係兩年咁短你都捱唔掂<br />\n咁你quit左做咩都係得失敗一條路<br />\n成世人都係淨係識quit<br />\n所以你拿拿聲quit完做隱青算"},{"pid":"6fd0ce18c285b8f38035bfd50a13cecad5209f27","tid":2511611,"uid":121636,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T07:17:10.000Z","msg":"巴打，禁多咗嘢起底制，睇你唔係玩膠，係講真<br />\n<br />\n唔好 quit 啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多工作根本唔駛你讀嗰科都做到，就係差你張沙紙，仲要理得你 2nd hon 定 3rd hon 甚至冇 hon 都係一視同行！"},{"pid":"ea7f00bcd0f871620809d235a82153c65f0b800a","tid":2511611,"uid":390508,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T07:22:07.000Z","msg":"Cls 唔好quit U咁on9 啦...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有好多人想讀大學都冇得讀 你就有得讀HKU 但係唔想讀要quit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢個世界真係好撚荒謬<br />\n<br />\n有得讀HKU唔該你好好珍惜"},{"pid":"a1abe920b061179801229e00e6e36913d8c4bac9","tid":2511611,"uid":168384,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T07:24:46.000Z","msg":"同意 冇興趣讀嚟都唔會用得着"},{"pid":"16de075f5198d0c02c1de1476e777b7cbb4105de","tid":2511611,"uid":121636,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime